4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp that allows individuals to become cybersecurity specialists in a shorter timeframe, even without prior knowledge. The program provides a foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, as well as practical skills to secure these environments. Students will also learn about cloud security, penetration testing, cyber threat intelligence analysis, and managing risks using data loss prevention strategies. The bootcamp has a duration of 16 weeks, with 3 live online classes per week and a class size of up to 16 people. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by multiple institutions. No previous experience is required to enroll in the bootcamp.

